---
---

<section class="final-cta" aria-label="Contacto">
	<div class="final-cta__inner">
		<h2 class="final-cta__title">
			¿Listo para construir tu próximo sistema?
		</h2>
		<p class="final-cta__copy">
			Diseñamos e implementamos software que escala con tu negocio.
			Cuéntanos tu reto y trazamos juntos el camino.
		</p>
		<a href="/contact" class="cta label-caps final-cta__btn">Hablemos</a>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.final-cta {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 4;
		background: var(--inverse-surface);
		color: var(--inverse-on-surface);
		padding: var(--stack-lg) var(--margin-edge);
	}

	.final-cta__inner {
		max-width: var(--container-max);
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		gap: var(--stack-md);
	}

	.final-cta__title {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px);
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		line-height: 1.05;
		max-width: 16ch;
	}

	.final-cta__copy {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 52ch;
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--inverse-on-surface);
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.final-cta__btn {
		background: var(--tertiary);
		color: var(--on-tertiary);
		padding: 14px 28px;
		border-radius: var(--r);
		transition:
			transform 200ms ease,
			filter 200ms ease;
	}

	.final-cta__btn:hover {
		transform: scale(1.02);
		filter: brightness(0.97);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.final-cta {
			padding: var(--stack-lg) var(--stack-md);
		}
	}
</style>
